    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i hear you on the security thing but it still feels like you're giving both sides equal weight when most data shows tariffs just act as a tax on regular people. like, can we really call it a \"debate\" if the economic evidence so heavily favors free trade? doesn't treating protectionism as a valid alternative just muddy the waters?",
